Several schools will focus on more classical modern languages, while others will teach languages that are considered the most important for the UK as of 2020, such as Mandarin Chinese or Japanese.
Whatever your child's interests, there will always be different languages to choose from in independent schools, with specialised teaching staff.
Independent schools in Scotland are committed to providing an environment for learning that will prepare children and equip them with the skills they need to succeed, whatever their future may be.
It is not possible to deny at this moment, in a global trading system, that languages continue to be fundamental for the future of the country, and this must be reflected in education.
